node.title: Multiple people injured in 'serious incident' in Auckland, reports of one dead
node.description: Police are at the scene of a 'serious incident' in the Auckland suburb of Mt Roskill.
node.content: ["Police are at the scene of a 'serious incident' in the Auckland suburb of Mt Roskill, after multiple people were injured and one reportedly killed.", "Police rushed to Glass Rd about 9:30pm on Thursday, where three people were found hurt. Two were taken to hospital.", "The NZ Herald reported one was dead.", "\"There will be a heavy police presence in the area while enquiries are made,\" police said.", "No arrests have been made. It is not clear yet if a firearm was involved.", "Newshub has contacted police for an update.", "\u00a0"]
